snippet.title: Squirrel with a Gun - Official Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2023
snippet.description:
Dan DeEntremont Productions released their second trailer for their upcoming sandbox game Squirrel with a Gun today during Summer of Gaming. The trailer features the squirrel's gun-toting origin story (of sorts), plenty of hilarious shenanigans, and most importantly: a Bond-like theme song for our furry protagonist.

#SummerOfGaming #IGN
